27 March 2020 Ministers representing the COVID -19 National Command Council will  update the nation on the status of the COVID 19 lockdown in South Africa. Members of the media are invited to cover the media briefing as follows: Date: Friday, 27 March 2020Time: 18h00Venue: Tshedimosetso House, GCIS Auditorium, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield in Pretoria NOTE TO MEDIA: In heeding the call of prohibiting a gathering of more than a hundred (100) people, ONLY 50 media practitioners will be allowed to attend and cover the briefing on a first come first served basis. RSVPs: Pheliswa Sebati Cell: 082 413 4609 E-mail: Pheliswa@gcis.gov.za Enquiries:  William Baloyi Cell: 083 390 7147